          <br />
          ðŸŽ¯ Match your CV to dream jobs<br />
          âœ¨ Craft compelling cover letters<br />
          ðŸš€ Get job-ready in minutes, not hours
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 text-center lg:text-left">
          <a
            href="/role-fit-index"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-accent-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-accent-700 transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            Check Your Role Fit Index for Free
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <style>
        @keyframes float {
          0% {
            transform: translateY(0px);
          }
          50% {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
          }
          100% {
            transform: translateY(0px);
          }
        }
        .fade-in svg {
          animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
      </style>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
